 User Side
✅ Register/Login (JWT, hashed passwords)

💬 Chat with a sentiment-aware AI (OpenAI or Hugging Face)

📊 Mood Tracker (based on user inputs and chat sentiment)

🧘 Personalized content: Breathing exercises, videos, articles

📁 Profile with mood history & resources accessed
